250
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
The life you always wanted.

251
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
With Reham. Your love.

252
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I knew about Reham and you, but I was foolish to think I could conquer you...

253
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
But no longer...

254
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I'm setting you free from what was never meant to be...

255
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I have no complaints or regret.

256
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
It's been three days!

257
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Why hasn't the money been transferred?

258
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
It's against the company's policy, sir.

259
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
The amount's too big to transfer to a personal accoun --
-Then, change the company's policy.

260
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
It's our company, and it'll be our policy.

261
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I'll need Madame's permission.

262
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
She's never transferred to her own account or M. Ashir's --
-And Madame Sofia's put me in-charge, right?

263
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
She's given me the right.

264
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
